cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.MM

The paper deals with computer vision and natural language processing techniques applied to medical image databases. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves text mining and natural language processing, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper involves unsupervised and supervised learning, which could place it in cs.IR (Information Retrieval) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper deals with medical images, which could also place it in cs.MM (Multimedia).
